# PMOMax App Guide (Updated)

## Introduction
PMOMax is a gold-themed, AI-powered PID builder for modern project teams. This guide covers all new features, workflows, and compliance updates.

## Main Features
- Unified input panel (paste, drop, upload)
- AI assistant for document editing
- Export to Word, PDF, JSON
- Health check endpoint
- SBOM and vulnerability reporting

## Workflow
1. Clear all state
2. Upload or paste data
3. Parse and edit
4. Export

## Compliance
- All Marketplace requirements met
- See README.md and metadata.json for details

